{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/vue/vue-devtools-initial-setting/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Soobing","author":"[Soobin Bak]","siteUrl":"https://soobing.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"soobing/soobing.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"soobing"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"93a37c21-c177-5e22-a82a-0a2154eff47a","excerpt":"이 동영상을 참고해서 공부중인데\n아래처럼 devtool을 설치했는데도 불구하고 에서도 안뜨고, 에서도 안뜬다!!!  문제 발생  해결 이 링크를 통해서 문제를 해결했는데,\nproduction 모드가 아닌 경우나 CDN을 통해서 vue를 가지고오는 경우 발생하는 모양이다. \n그래서 요렇게 devtools의 값을 true로 셋팅해줘야한다. 나는 main.js에다가 js를 몰아서 작업중이라 위의 코드를 main.js에 넣어줬다! 파일 URL…","html":"<p>이 <a href=\"https://www.vuemastery.com/courses/intro-to-vue-js/vue-instance\">동영상</a>을 참고해서 공부중인데\n아래처럼 devtool을 설치했는데도 불구하고 <code class=\"language-text\">개발자도구</code>에서도 안뜨고, <code class=\"language-text\">panel</code>에서도 안뜬다!!! </p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-발생\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EB%B0%9C%EC%83%9D\" aria-label=\"문제 발생 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 발생</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 826px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 69.33333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"문제\"\n        title=\"문제\"\n        src=\"/static/4867b2eac9e5365012ba310b307b9b13/6a6e9/vue-devtools-setting-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4867b2eac9e5365012ba310b307b9b13/5a46d/vue-devtools-setting-1.png 300w,\n/static/4867b2eac9e5365012ba310b307b9b13/0a47e/vue-devtools-setting-1.png 600w,\n/static/4867b2eac9e5365012ba310b307b9b13/6a6e9/vue-devtools-setting-1.png 826w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 826px) 100vw, 826px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"해결\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0\" aria-label=\"해결 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>해결</h1>\n<p>이 <a href=\"https://github.com/vuejs/vue-devtools/issues/190\">링크</a>를 통해서 문제를 해결했는데,\nproduction 모드가 아닌 경우나 CDN을 통해서 vue를 가지고오는 경우 발생하는 모양이다.\n그래서 요렇게 devtools의 값을 true로 셋팅해줘야한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">Vue<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>config<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>devtools <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>나는 main.js에다가 js를 몰아서 작업중이라 위의 코드를 main.js에 넣어줬다!</p>\n<h2 id=\"파일-url에-대한-엑세스-허용\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-url%EC%97%90-%EB%8C%80%ED%95%9C-%EC%97%91%EC%84%B8%EC%8A%A4-%ED%97%88%EC%9A%A9\" aria-label=\"파일 url에 대한 엑세스 허용 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>파일 URL에 대한 엑세스 허용</h2>\n<p>위에처럼 했는데도 안될때는 <code class=\"language-text\">확장 프로그램 관리</code>에 들어가서\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 642px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"확장 프로그램 관리\"\n        title=\"확장 프로그램 관리\"\n        src=\"/static/655066bdcf9fb1b688fa918e14b8272b/1bba8/vue-devtools-setting-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/655066bdcf9fb1b688fa918e14b8272b/5a46d/vue-devtools-setting-5.png 300w,\n/static/655066bdcf9fb1b688fa918e14b8272b/0a47e/vue-devtools-setting-5.png 600w,\n/static/655066bdcf9fb1b688fa918e14b8272b/1bba8/vue-devtools-setting-5.png 642w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 642px) 100vw, 642px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">파일 URL에 대한 엑세스 허용</code>을 해준다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1086px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 20.666666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"확장 프로그램 관리\"\n        title=\"확장 프로그램 관리\"\n        src=\"/static/62f56a11a59a06c55a80c03d4286d6e3/f3a19/vue-devtools-setting-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/62f56a11a59a06c55a80c03d4286d6e3/5a46d/vue-devtools-setting-2.png 300w,\n/static/62f56a11a59a06c55a80c03d4286d6e3/0a47e/vue-devtools-setting-2.png 600w,\n/static/62f56a11a59a06c55a80c03d4286d6e3/f3a19/vue-devtools-setting-2.png 1086w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1086px) 100vw, 1086px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"인증\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B8%EC%A6%9D\" aria-label=\"인증 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>인증</h1>\n<p>vue 아이콘을 클릭하면 제대로 로드되었고, 패널도 확인해보라는 것을 알 수 있다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 824px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"vue\"\n        title=\"vue\"\n        src=\"/static/169d44ecedf7e55714cccb03d96c7e52/c1c45/vue-devtools-setting-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/169d44ecedf7e55714cccb03d96c7e52/5a46d/vue-devtools-setting-4.png 300w,\n/static/169d44ecedf7e55714cccb03d96c7e52/0a47e/vue-devtools-setting-4.png 600w,\n/static/169d44ecedf7e55714cccb03d96c7e52/c1c45/vue-devtools-setting-4.png 824w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 824px) 100vw, 824px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>이렇게 누르면 쫘라란 ~ 패널이 생긴다!\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 426px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100.33333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"vue\"\n        title=\"vue\"\n        src=\"/static/eeaf426f48a386e9e651304ef01723bb/531e1/vue-devtools-setting-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/eeaf426f48a386e9e651304ef01723bb/5a46d/vue-devtools-setting-3.png 300w,\n/static/eeaf426f48a386e9e651304ef01723bb/531e1/vue-devtools-setting-3.png 426w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 426px) 100vw, 426px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>이렇게 나의 첫 vue 포스팅을 마칩니다. ^ㅡ^</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"😈vue devtools pannel이 보이지 않는 이슈","date":"May 03, 2020","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"src":"/static/4867b2eac9e5365012ba310b307b9b13/ee604/vue-devtools-setting-1.png"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/vue/vue-devtools-initial-setting/","previous"